  "text": "No deficits were detected in any of the studies using measures of visual/spatial skills, visual/motor skills, visual-spatial perception, and/or visual-spatial organization. [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] 31 Comparing carriers with noncarriers, no significant group mean score differences were detected. [CITATION_3] 30 In addition, Thompson et al. 31 determined that the mean score of a group of 12 premutation carriers was within the normal range. None of these studies analyzed the correlation of repeat length with spatial ability scores.",
